    IFVAR WEALTH >= 300
      SUB WEALTH 300
      EQUAL FLAG1 2
      ECHO PLAYER The violinist smiles and begins to play.
      ECHO OTHERS The violinist walks over to %N's table and begins to play.
      PLREVENT 1
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL The violinist pulls his bow across his strings, playing a melody that is beautiful and haunting.
      PLREVENT 1
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO PLAYER The violinist leans over and plays an exceptionally moving theme, seemingly especially for you.
      ECHO OTHERS The violinist leans over %N's table and plays an exceptionally moving theme.
      PLREVENT 2
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL Stepping up the pace and the tempo, the violinist begins to sweat as he pours his energy into his song.
      PLREVENT 1
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL With a shout, the violinist finishes his song, flushed with exertion. He smiles bashfully, takes a brief bow, and begins to patrol the tables again.
      EQUAL FLAG1 0
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
